{"tid":580876,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界場地單車錦標賽】李慧詩首奪凱林賽銀牌","createTime":"2018-03-05T00:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T15:33:50.000Z","uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa8215699b2781ad222981f0622083e82513800","tid":580876,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180304/large/1520174320_4cd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180304%2Flarge%2F1520174320_4cd5.jpg&h=f8264f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180304/large/1520177374_8b9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180304%2Flarge%2F1520177374_8b9e.jpg&h=a617538f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180304/large/1520173266_bc60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180304%2Flarge%2F1520173266_bc60.jpg&h=81224c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180304/large/1520177375_de82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180304%2Flarge%2F1520177375_de82.jpg&h=a361300c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在荷蘭舉行的最後一天世界場地單車錦標賽，香港女車神李慧詩帶來驚喜，對上兩個比賽都沒有獎牌的慧詩，在女子凱林賽決賽，憑臨尾一個圈奮力從後趕上，她終於奪得一面銀牌，這亦是她個人第五面世錦賽獎牌！賽後她終於笑了，亦見到港隊總教練沈金康也笑了！<br />\n<br />\n翻查李慧詩在世錦賽的往績，她曾於2013年白俄羅斯世錦賽奪得一金（500米計時賽)一銅(爭先賽)，再在2016年倫敦世錦賽奪得500米計時賽銀牌，去年在香港主場的世錦賽，她奪得爭先賽銅牌，今次凱林賽銀牌是她個人世錦賽第五面獎牌，對一月才宣佈為2020東奧的她打了一支強心針。<br />\n<br />\n而在賽前備受看好衛冕的禾高，出乎意外，在三圈的比賽，她都未能找到有利位置，最後由21歲的比利時車手Nicky Degrendele奪冠，Nicky去年在香港世錦賽奪得此賽項的銅牌，今年大躍進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180304/57904519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180304%2F57904519&d=Sx7f%2Ff9hdAPMr%2Bp%2Fh%2F4ymVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=36b6a39c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180304%2F57904519&h=b3b3440c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180304/57904519</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5101bcf0f3f02f407815ba83fe510343f8102e7f","tid":580876,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"比人睇低做underdog反而有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}